('w_shopping_B2_03','premium','/ˈpriːmiəm/','adjective','프리미엄의','Of higher quality and usually higher price.','This is a {premium} product line.','이건 프리미엄 제품 라인이에요.','premium','B2','shopping',4,'premium luxury product'),
