('w_environment_C1_29','ecological footprint','/ˌiːkəˈlɒdʒɪkəl ˈfʊtprɪnt/','noun phrase','생태 발자국','The demand placed on Earth''s resources by human activities.','Reducing your {ecological footprint} helps the planet.','생태 발자국을 줄이면 지구에 도움이 돼요.','ecological footprint','C1','environment',1,'ecological footprint earth resource lifestyle eco'),
('w_environment_C1_30','planetary health','/ˈplænɪtɛri hɛlθ/','noun phrase','지구 건강','The health of human civilization and the natural systems it depends on.','{Planetary health} links human wellbeing to Earth''s ecosystems.','지구 건강은 인간의 웰빙과 지구 생태계를 연결해요.','planetary health','C1','environment',1,'planetary health earth ecosystem human wellbeing'),
