('w_environment_C2_01','radiative forcing','/ˈreɪdiətɪv ˈfɔːrsɪŋ/','noun phrase','복사 강제력','The change in energy in the atmosphere caused by greenhouse gases.','{Radiative forcing} from CO2 is the dominant warming driver.','이산화탄소의 복사 강제력이 온난화의 주된 원인이에요.','radiative forcing','C2','environment',1,'radiative forcing energy atmosphere CO2 science'),
('w_environment_C2_02','thermohaline circulation','/ˌθɜːrmoʊˈheɪlaɪn ˌsɜːrkjʊˈleɪʃən/','noun phrase','열염 순환','The ocean circulation driven by temperature and salinity differences.','{Thermohaline circulation} regulates global climate patterns.','열염 순환은 전 지구적 기후 패턴을 조절해요.','thermohaline circulation','C2','environment',1,'thermohaline ocean current map global climate'),
('w_environment_C2_03','albedo feedback','/ælˈbiːdoʊ ˈfiːdbæk/','noun phrase','알베도 피드백','The amplification of warming as ice loss reduces surface reflectivity.','{Albedo feedback} accelerates Arctic warming.','알베도 피드백이 북극 온난화를 가속화해요.','albedo feedback','C2','environment',1,'albedo feedback ice arctic warming science'),
('w_environment_C2_04','cryosphere dynamics','/ˈkraɪoʊsfɪər daɪˈnæmɪks/','noun phrase','빙권 역학','The physical processes governing ice and frozen water on Earth.','{Cryosphere dynamics} influence sea level projections.','빙권 역학은 해수면 전망에 영향을 미쳐요.','cryosphere dynamics','C2','environment',1,'cryosphere dynamics ice model science arctic'),
