('w_environment_C2_06','tipping point','/ˈtɪpɪŋ pɔɪnt/','noun phrase','티핑 포인트','A threshold beyond which a system undergoes irreversible change.','The Amazon may be approaching a {tipping point}.','아마존은 티핑 포인트에 가까워지고 있을 수 있어요.','tipping point','C2','environment',1,'tipping point climate threshold change irreversible'),
('w_environment_C2_07','teleconnection','/ˌtɛlɪkəˈnɛkʃən/','noun','원격 상관','The correlation between weather patterns in distant parts of the world.','{Teleconnections} link El Nino events to global weather anomalies.','원격 상관은 엘니뇨 현상을 전 세계 이상 기상과 연결해요.','teleconnection','C2','environment',1,'teleconnection El Nino weather pattern globe science'),
('w_environment_C2_08','planetary boundary','/ˈplænɪtɛri ˈbaʊndəri/','noun phrase','행성 한계','The safe operating limits within which humanity can thrive.','We have crossed several {planetary boundaries}.','우리는 이미 몇 가지 행성 한계를 넘었어요.','planetary boundary','C2','environment',1,'planetary boundary earth limit science policy'),
