('w_work_B1_01','strategy','/ˈstrætɪdʒi/','noun','전략','A plan of action designed to achieve a long-term goal.','We need a clear {strategy}.','명확한 전략이 필요해요.','strategy','B1','work',2,'strategy plan chess business'),
