('w_work_B1_03','milestone','/ˈmaɪlstoʊn/','noun','주요 이정표','A significant event in a project''s progress.','We reached our first {milestone}.','첫 번째 이정표에 도달했어요.','milestone','B1','work',2,'milestone achievement progress timeline'),
