('w_work_B1_05','delegate','/ˈdelɪɡeɪt/','verb','위임하다','To assign responsibility to another person.','You should {delegate} some tasks.','일부 업무를 위임해야 해요.','delegate','B1','work',2,'delegate authority manager team'),
